  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when he-- he walked with the children to the chambers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sanatorium, it was a-- a nice building, and Jewish-- all Jewish workers there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember, there was a good friend of mine, he was the electrician.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they have, they have a-- a generator to run for the electricity on the whole farm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Kanisczer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, all Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was for Jewish and-- and from Jewish people, the rich people in Lodz, where they-- where they--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where they give money for this, only Jewish, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I suppose anybody, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because Lodz was very much, very rich Jewish factories, very rich people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kohn was textile industry, the biggest I think who was in Poland in this time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We call this [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody told me the son, Oskar, went somewhere into Sweden or somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he was a Swedish consulate before in-- in Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But what's happened further, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We read about it, and know about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And many Jews from Germany run to Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I was in Germany later on, they told me there-- there was not a good invitation from the Polish Jews for the German Jews, who have some [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know how to tell you.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[POLISH] They are not-- not satisfied with the handling, the-- the German Jews when they come from Germany to Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were not very good, not very welcome.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is what they told me when I was in Germany later on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing special, what was happening I remember, it was the-- the Hitler-- I don't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were there in Poland-- they were-- they were hunting in Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
